| Quantum Computing Playground | Simulator | Quantum Computing | A web-based platform that provides a visual interface for users to simulate quantum computing circuits and algorithms. | [Link](https://quantum-computing.ibm.com/) |
| Artificial Intelligence Podcast | Podcast | Artificial Intelligence | A series of podcasts hosted by AI experts who discuss the latest advances and research in the field of AI. | [Link](https://lexfridman.com/ai/) |
Use the following JavaScript code to sort the table by subfield in alphabetical order:
var table = document.querySelector('table');
var tbody = table.querySelector('tbody');
var rows = Array.from(tbody.children);
rows.sort((a, b) => {
  if (a.children[2].textContent < b.children[2].textContent) {
    return -1;
  }
  if (a.children[2].textContent > b.children[2].textContent) {
    return 1;
  }
  return 0;
});
tbody.innerHTML = '';
tbody.append(...rows);
